8. Articles

The following tasks needs to be achieved while building a ML model
shared for a task
(i)  We need all the records in “Article_Description” and “Full_Article” to be cleaned.Remove the html tags

(ii) Merge the columns “Heading”, “Article_Description” and “Full_Article” separated by space and place the merged text in a new column name “Preprocessed_Text”

(iii) Remove stopwords and punctuation for all the records in the column  “Preprocessed_Text”

(iv) Remove the leading or trailing whitespaces for all the records in the column  “Preprocessed_Text”


